descriptionHtml:
Mega Radio 7 is Your personal music teacher.
With the music that we present on this radio you will always have a good mood. It acts on every cell of your body, positively.

We Present:

NEW YORK CAFE
There is nowhere in the world, to find a better choice of music, than the one you are listening on New York Jazz Café. Specially selected Modern Ambient Jazz, Slow Groove, Soul Music, Latin Jazz, Afro Cuban… a thousand jazz stars all around the world. With the music that we present on this radio you will always have a good mood. It acts positively on every cell of your body.
If you love music, you will be a member of our Club forever. Enjoy!

GROOVE SALAD
Groove Salad with an original taste. Groove Jazz, Funky Groove, dramatic beats, powerful drums, guitar riffs, a powerful saxophone that breaks down tension in your body and a rhythm that will keep you moving all day and all night. This is the real Groove salad, unique in the world, prepared in our music kitcen.
Nothing else compares!

LOVE RADIO
If you are a romantic, be sure to listen to Love Radio. The best performances in the last 4 decades, specially selected songs of the greatest names in the history of music. Hits that love all generations, will take you to a sensual place.

DISCO FEVER
Do you want to dance? Everything from the music that was a master hit in all discos on the planet from the 70's until today. On songs you always dance whenever you hear them. The top of disco music, non stop plays for you in one place and one radio. On Disco Fever. Extra selected podium for you!
Best of the best dance hits!

ALCOHOL
This is the perfect radio for all those moments when you want to drown yourself in music. Get your heart excited, or your soul crying, dwell on the past but also be happy about the future. Balkan mix of greatest songs ever made. Everything for singing.
Enjoy out Alcohol Radio.
